						Non qu&ograve;, sed qu&agrave;: Lipsius.
					</marginalia_text>
					<person name="Machiavelli"/>
					<person name="Lipsius"/>
				</position>
			</language>
			<translation>
				Not why, but how: Machiavelli.
				Not how, but why: Lipsius.
			</translation>
		</marginalia>
		
